{"tid":2337549,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"民權組織：至少7無關案件交國安處","createTime":"2020-12-23T11:03:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-23T11:03:38.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"af576da71005f4d53a2575e9c32ddc6cb3fc3618","tid":2337549,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T11:03:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201223/LV4Z65SNSVHDXNGXDJYLISZDQI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201223%2FLV4Z65SNSVHDXNGXDJYLISZDQI%2F&d=djscsuFvXcghIMf2lgFVp7AecByD1k%2Bs4QbbWwjAUoc%3D&h=a886d82c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201223%2FLV4Z65SNSVHDXNGXDJYLISZDQI%2F&h=9bd272dd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201223/LV4Z65SNSVHDXNGXDJYLISZDQI/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n民權組織：至少7無關案件交國安處<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/ejAvQIi9vBPznNw1rW9KRmLCSvc=/1000x563/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/FG5TVBRVZBAITPBZEGJ6GVS2YI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FejAvQIi9vBPznNw1rW9KRmLCSvc%3D%2F1000x563%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FFG5TVBRVZBAITPBZEGJ6GVS2YI.jpg&h=c39e3d0a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■「美國隊長2.0」早前被警方以港版國安法起訴。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】港版國安法實施近半年，多人被捕被控。民權觀察就港版國安法發表報告顯示，至上月底，警方以國安法罪名作出至少27次拘捕，其中三人被起訴，另有至少七宗不涉及國安法的案件由國安處調查。黃廠因為產品設計及政治立場停運，引證國安法帶來的寒蟬效應。<br />\n<br />\n民權觀察就國安法生效後的。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n寒蟬效應影響民間商業活動<br />\n<br />\n報告指出，有最少七宗不涉及國安法的刑事案件亦由警方國安處介入調查，包括國安法生效前的涉嫌罪行，令人質疑是否濫權。報告以人民力量「慢必」譚得志為例，他所涉控罪無關國安法，卻由擁有不清和不受審查強大權力的國安處調查，相關權力有可能被濫用。報告亦關注譚得志個案轉介至國安法指定法官審理，令人對既有的訴訟程序及政策產生疑問。<br />\n<br />\n民權觀察認為，政府及司法機。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n國安法引起的寒蟬效應更影響民間商業活動，其中公開支持反送中運動的黃廠，因。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n保安局稱警方作出拘捕是基於證據和嚴格按照法律進行，與政治背景及。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/evYxvylLOavYVwfT29b3jHnPnK8=/484x854/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/O3YONL3RMRF47AN7GONMJJYLII.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FevYxvylLOavYVwfT29b3jHnPnK8%3D%2F484x854%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FO3YONL3RMRF47AN7GONMJJYLII.gif&h=076fb774&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}